INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [t].[CreatedById] = [a0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProjectPhases] AS [p] ON [t].[ProjectPhaseId] = [p].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [MaintenanceRequests] AS [m] ON [t].[MaintenanceRequestId] = [m].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[ActualCost], [p].[Budget], [p].[ClientId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[EndDate], [p].[Location], [p].[Name], [p].[ProjectManagerId], [p].[StartDate], [p].[Status], [p].[UpdatedAt], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[Address], [a].[Company], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[FirstName], [a].[IsActive], [a].[LastName], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[Phone], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[Role], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UpdatedAt] AS [UpdatedAt0], [a].[UserName], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[AccessFailedCount] AS [AccessFailedCount0], [a0].[Address] AS [Address0], [a0].[Company] AS [Company0], [a0].[ConcurrencyStamp] AS [ConcurrencyStamp0], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[Email] AS [Email0], [a0].[EmailConfirmed] AS [EmailConfirmed0], [a0].[FirstName] AS [FirstName0], [a0].[IsActive] AS [IsActive0], [a0].[LastName] AS [LastName0], [a0].[LockoutEnabled] AS [LockoutEnabled0], [a0].[LockoutEnd] AS [LockoutEnd0], [a0].[NormalizedEmail] AS [NormalizedEmail0], [a0].[NormalizedUserName] AS [NormalizedUserName0], [a0].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash0], [a0].[Phone] AS [Phone0], [a0].[PhoneNumber] AS [PhoneNumber0], [a0].[PhoneNumberConfirmed] AS [PhoneNumberConfirmed0], [a0].[Role] AS [Role0], [a0].[SecurityStamp] AS [SecurityStamp0], [a0].[TwoFactorEnabled] AS [TwoFactorEnabled0], [a0].[UpdatedAt] AS [UpdatedAt1], [a0].[UserName] AS [UserName0]
    FROM [Projects] AS [p]
    LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [p].[ProjectManagerId] = [a].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [p].[ClientId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [s]
LEFT JOIN [ProjectPhases] AS [p0] ON [s].[Id] = [p0].[ProjectId]
LEFT JOIN [MaintenanceRequests] AS [m] ON [s].[Id] = [m].[ProjectId]
LEFT JOIN [Documents] AS [d] ON [s].[Id] = [d].[ProjectId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[AssignedAt], [p1].[ContractorId], [p1].[HourlyRate], [p1].[ProjectId], [p1].[Specialization], [p1].[Status], [p1].[UnassignedAt], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [a1].[AccessFailedCount], [a1].[Address], [a1].[Company], [a1].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a1].[CreatedAt], [a1].[Email], [a1].[EmailConfirmed], [a1].[FirstName], [a1].[IsActive], [a1].[LastName], [a1].[LockoutEnabled], [a1].[LockoutEnd], [a1].[NormalizedEmail], [a1].[NormalizedUserName], [a1].[PasswordHash], [a1].[Phone], [a1].[PhoneNumber], [a1].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a1].[Role], [a1].[SecurityStamp], [a1].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a1].[UpdatedAt], [a1].[UserName]
    FROM [ProjectContractors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a1] ON [p1].[ContractorId] = [a1].[Id]
